    "type": "NOTE",
    "url": null,
    "content": "## Two Pointers Technique\n\nUsed for problems involving sorted arrays or pairs.\n\n### Pattern\n```\nleft = 0, right = n - 1\nwhile left < right:\n    if condition: move left\n    else: move right\n```\n\n### When to use\n- Finding pairs with a given sum\n- Removing duplicates\n- Reversing in-place",
    "labId": "lab_dsa_tu",
