  {
    "id": "res_algo_ec_dp_snippet",
    "title": "Coin Change – Solution Template",
    "type": "CODE_SNIPPET",
    "url": null,
    "content": "```python\ndef coinChange(coins, amount):\n    dp = [float('inf')] * (amount + 1)\n    dp[0] = 0\n    for coin in coins:\n        for x in range(coin, amount + 1):\n            dp[x] = min(dp[x], dp[x - coin] + 1)\n    return dp[amount] if dp[amount] != float('inf') else -1\n```",
    "labId": "lab_algo_ec",
    "assignmentId": "assign_algo_dp",
    "uploadedById": "user_inst2_instructor_1",
    "isPublic": false
